 to Defra / DECC's GHG Conversion Factors for Company Reporting |date= 2012 }}\n* {{cite book |url= http://www.gci.org.uk/Documents/Aviation-and-Climate-Change_.pdf |title= Climate Change and Aviation \u2014 Issues, Challenges and Solutions |author= [[Stefan G\u00f6ssling]] and Paul Upham |publisher= [[Earthscan]] |date= 2009 |isbn= 978-1-84407-619-2 }}\n* {{cite news |url= https://www.iea.org/reports/tracking-transport-2019/aviation |title= Tracking Transport: Aviation |date= May 2019 |publisher= [[International Energy Agency]]}}\n\n; Articles\n* {{cite news |url= http://aviationweek.com/commercial-aviation/opinion-uncomfortable-truth-about-aviation-emissions |title= Opinion: The Uncomfortable Truth About Aviation Emissions |date= 10 August 2016 |author= Antoine Gelain |work= Aviation Week & Space Technology}}\n\n{{Global warming|state=collapsed}}\n{{Human impact on the environment|state=collapsed}}\n{{Commercial air travel}}\n{{Portal bar|Aviation|Environment}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Environmental Impact Of Aviation}}\n[[Category:Air pollution|Aviation]]\n[[Category:Aviation and the environment| ]]\n[[Category:Environmental impact by source|Aviation]]\n", "name_user": "99.229.12.135", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Environmental_impact_of_aviation"}
